==English==
===Noun===
'''asymptote''' (''plural'' '''asymptotes''')

#(''mathematics'') A [[straight line]] which a [[curve]] approaches arbitrarily closely, but never reaches, as they go to [[infinity]].  The limit of the curve, its tangent "at infinity".

