*Dutch: [[:nl:asymptoot|asymptoot]] ''m''
* [[Ido]]: [[asimptoto]]
*Russian: [[асимптота]] (asimptóta) {{f}}
*Swedish: [[asymptot]] ''c''
*Portuguese: [[assíntota]]

